des:
The Awesome 2018 Winter Olympics Trivia Game provides fun and information to people who know 2018 Winter Olympics for all ages.

The 2018 Winter Olympics Trivia will ask you 7 questions with 4 answers to choose from and you will have to tell the Answer number.

Could you enable "2018 Winter Olympics Trivia" and just say "Open Winter Olympics Trivia" to your Alexa~
